📝 Developer Task: Implement “שאלון לברוקרים” Form

1. General Layout
Theme:
Dark mode (background: #18181C or similar, text: white or near-white).
Max width: 900px (centered, responsive).
Font: Use a modern sans-serif (e.g., Inter, Open Sans, or system default).
2. Header
Text: שאלון לברוקרים
Font size: 2rem (32px)
Font weight: 600–700
Spacing: 40px below header before form starts
3. Form Structure
Form sections:
Contact Info (שם משפחה, טלפון, Email)
Area/Lending City (אזור פתיחת תיק רצוי, עיר ליבה רצויה)
Work (עבודה)
Additional Info (מידע נוסף)
Section headers:
Font size: 1.4rem (22px), bold, 24px top margin above
Underline/Divider: Optional, subtle 1px line in #292932 or 12px spacing below header.
4. Form Inputs
a) General

Input fields:
Height: 48px
Border-radius: 8px
Border: 1.5px solid #34343A
Background: #232328
Padding-left/right: 16px
Text color: #F6F6F9
Font-size: 1rem (16px)
Spacing:
24px between rows
20px between fields in same row (except mobile)
Responsive: stack vertically on <700px width
Labels:
Above input
Font-size: 0.9rem (15px)
Color: #B8B8C5
4px spacing below label
b) Dropdowns

Trigger:
Height: 48px (same as input)
Border, background, padding as above
Chevron/down arrow on left (RTL)
Dropdown list:
Min width: matches trigger
Max height: 200px (scroll if overflow)
Option height: 44px
Hover: background #2D2D33
Selected: #3A3A44
c) Radio Buttons (כן / לא)

Style:
Use custom button style (not browser default)
Size: 40px width, 40px height
Border-radius: 8px
Font-size: 1rem
Selected: background #34343A, text #FFF
d) Text Area

Height: 64px
Min rows: 3
Max rows: 6
Same style as input
e) Checkbox

Custom design:
20px square, border-radius: 4px, border: 1.5px solid #34343A
When checked: background #34343A, checkmark white
f) Buttons (שליחה, חזור)

Width: 150px
Height: 48px
Font-size: 1.1rem (17px)
Border-radius: 8px
Primary: Background #34343A, text #FFF
Secondary: Transparent bg, border: 1.5px solid #34343A, text #FFF
Spacing: 20px between buttons
5. Special Elements
Phone input:
Prefix for country flag (+972)
Use input mask for phone numbers
Email:
Placeholder: "הזן אימייל"
Select search:
All dropdowns must have an internal search box (14px font)
6. Responsiveness
On mobile (<700px):
All elements stack vertically
Reduce paddings to 10–12px
Buttons and inputs full width
7. Accessibility
Labels linked to inputs
Tab order logical
Error states: Border color #FF5252, show error text below in #FF5252, 13px font.
8. Examples / Visual Guidance
Pixel-perfect:
Input height: exactly 48px
Label to input: 4px
Section margin: 32px between sections
Buttons: 48px tall, 8px radius
9. Nice-to-haves
Transitions:
Focus: border color animates to #F9D23B (or brand color) in 0.15s
Dropdown: smooth expand/collapse
Summary Example (for Developer)

“All input fields are 48px tall, with 16px horizontal padding and 8px rounded corners. Font size for inputs is 16px, labels are 15px. Section headers are 22px bold. There is 24px vertical space between each field, and on mobile all elements stack vertically with full width. Use #232328 as input background, #34343A for borders, and #F6F6F9 for text. Dropdowns have search inside, with options 44px tall. Buttons are 150x48px, primary #34343A, secondary transparent with a border. Ensure all form controls are accessible, focus has an animated border color transition. See attached screenshot for spacing reference.”
